```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User App
    participant Load Balancer
    participant Traffic Data Ingestion Service
    participant Route Calculation Service
    participant Congestion Detection Service
    participant User Profile Service
    participant Notification Service
    participant WhatsApp API
    participant Database

    User App->>Load Balancer: Traffic data update request
    Load Balancer->>Traffic Data Ingestion Service: Route data
    Traffic Data Ingestion Service->>Route Calculation Service: Get route data
    Route Calculation Service->>Database: Query Routes
    Database-->>Route Calculation Service: Route Data
    Route Calculation Service-->>Traffic Data Ingestion Service: Return Routes
    Traffic Data Ingestion Service->>Congestion Detection Service: Analyze traffic data
    Congestion Detection Service->>Database: Query historical traffic data
    Database-->>Congestion Detection Service: Historical traffic data
    Congestion Detection Service-->>Traffic Data Ingestion Service: Report congestion
    Traffic Data Ingestion Service->>User Profile Service: Get user details based on routes
    User Profile Service->>Database: Query User Profiles
    Database-->>User Profile Service: User Profiles
    User Profile Service-->>Traffic Data Ingestion Service: Return User details (WhatsApp Number, Preferred Routes)
    Traffic Data Ingestion Service->>Notification Service: Trigger Notification
    Notification Service->>WhatsApp API: Send Notification
    WhatsApp API->>User App: Traffic Update Notification
```